name: Embroidered Felt Ornaments --- Choose one
description:
Here is our new collection of felt ornaments – SANTA’S FELTERS!

They are carefully embroidered Christmas tree ornaments that are embellished with seed beads and sequins.

The ornaments are made of recycled felt (can you believe it used to be a plastic bottle!) and stuffed with fiberfill. They hang from thin ribbon and are about 2 ½” x 1 ¾” in size.

Perfect for trees and arrangements that can be reached by children and pets! It is made without glass or metal and cannot brake into dangerous pieces. You do have to be aware of the small beads, but those won’t come off that easily.

Your choice of one! Please let me know in notes to seller if you would like the pink and blue Christmas Tree, brown and pink wreath, green and brown classical ornament, brown and purple present, orange and blue stocking, or blue and maroon Candy Cane. 

Each one is truly unique and one of a kind!

name: Embroidered Christmas Tree Felt Ornament --- Purple, Grey
description:
Here is our new collection of felt ornaments – SANTA’S FELTERS!

This carefully embroidered Christmas tree ornament is adorned with blue, orange, and red embroidery yarn, tiny white pearls, and a small blue star sequin as tree topper.

The ornament is made of recycled felt (can you believe it used to be a plastic bottle) and stuffed with fiberfill. It hangs from a lavender thin ribbon and is about 2 ½” x 1 ¾” in size.

Perfect for trees and arrangements that can be reached by children and pets! It is made without glass or metal and cannot brake into dangerous pieces. You do have to be aware of the small beads, but those won’t come off that easily.

This piece is truly unique and one of a kind!
